1. get input number from user and keep reprompting
   for a valid positive integer using a do..while() loop.
   Return number once a valid number has been entered.

2. Call the collatz function on the valid positive integer
   using recursion to count how many steps to get back to 1 from the
   number.
   1 is added to each recursive call.

3. Print the amount of steps to bet back to 1 from number.